<refnamediv>
<refname>pldebug</refname>
<refpurpose>output a UnixPlot stream in ascii</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>
<!-- body begins here -->
<refsynopsisdiv xml:id='synopsis'>
<cmdsynopsis>
  <command>pldebug</command>    
    <arg choice='opt'>-v </arg>
    <arg choice='opt'><replaceable>unix_plot</replaceable></arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>


<refsect1 xml:id='description'><title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<para>Outputs a UnixPlot (see
<citerefentry><refentrytitle>plot</refentrytitle><manvolnum>5</manvolnum></citerefentry>)
stream in ascii for debugging.  If the
<option>-v</option>
option is given, a summary of plot command usage is given at the
end of the file.  Standard input is read if a file name is not supplied.</para>
</refsect1>

